interpretation: The "woman: blond hair" card represents a confident and charismatic individual who is not afraid to take charge. This person may have a natural ability to lead others and inspire them to reach their full potential. They are often seen as the life of the party and enjoy socializing with friends and meeting new people. However, their outgoing nature can sometimes come off as brash or overpowering to others. It is important for them to be mindful of their actions and how they may affect those around them.
